## ğŸ¯ Feature & RegTech Pain Point

Australian founders frequently miss regulatory filings because deadlines are tracked in spreadsheets, emails, or a founderâ€™s memory.

This demo solves one specific pain point:

> â€œShow me all compliance deadlines that are upcoming or overdue, allow me to tick them off, and make sure I donâ€™t forget anything.â€

The feature includes:

- List of regulatory deadlines
- Clear **overdue / due soon / upcoming** labels
- Colour indicators (ğŸ”´ overdue / ğŸŸ¢ upcoming or completed)
- One-click **Mark done**
- A popup that summarises **overdue + due-soon deadlines** when the user opens the app

Small feature â€” **big impact** on fines, stress, and accountant time.

