## ğŸ§± Architecture Overview

| Layer      | Technology |
|-----------|------------|
| Frontend  | React + Vite |
| Backend   | Go (in-memory storage) |
| Database  | None â€” simple and free to run |
| Deployment | Frontend on **Vercel**, Backend on **Render** |

### Backend

- Exposes REST API endpoints:
  - `GET /api/deadlines`
  - `POST /api/deadlines`
  - `POST /api/deadlines/:id/complete`
  - `GET /api/deadlines/summary`
- Stores deadlines in memory (no DB)
- Seeds real AU regulatory obligations as sample data

### Frontend

- Pages and components:
  - `DeadlinesPage`
  - `DeadlineForm`
  - `DeadlineList`
  - `DeadlineItem`
  - `OverdueSummaryModal`
- State management via custom hook `useDeadlines`
- Optimistic UI when marking as done
- Environment variable for backend URL

